---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About — The Local Match Co." description="About The Local Match Co. — professional matchmaking franchise built on 25 years of experience.">
  <Breadcrumbs items={[
    { label: 'Home', href: '/' },
    { label: 'About' }
  ]} />
  <article class="about">
    <h1>About The Local Match Co.</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      The Local Match Co. is a franchise platform that helps qualified operators launch 
      professional matchmaking services in their own city — built on 25 years of proven 
      methodology from 412 Singles in Pittsburgh.
    </p>

    <h2>Our Story</h2>
    <p>
      For 25 years, Rob Vargas has been making introductions in Pittsburgh — quietly, personally,
      one conversation at a time. While dating apps got bigger and algorithms got smarter, he kept 
      doing the same thing: sitting across the table from someone who was genuinely ready for a 
      relationship, understanding what they were looking for, and going to find it.
    </p>
    <p>
      Now, for the first time, he's opening that model up to other cities.
    </p>

    <h2>This Blog</h2>
    <p>
      This blog shares our thinking on matchmaking, relationships, and building a business 
      you believe in. We write for future franchise operators, for people curious about 
      professional matchmaking, and for anyone who believes that human connection deserves 
      a better infrastructure than a swipe.
    </p>

    <div class="cta-section">
      <h2>Interested in Your City?</h2>
      <p>We take one operator per metro area. If you've been thinking about this, now's the time.</p>
      <a href="https://thelocalmatch.com/#invest" class="cta-btn" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        Learn About Franchise Opportunities →
      </a>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about { max-width: 42rem; }
  .about h1 { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .lead {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--fg);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .about p { line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .cta-section {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: rgba(139, 26, 26, 0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(139, 26, 26, 0.3);
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
  }
  .cta-section h2 { margin-top: 0; }
  .cta-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    background: var(--accent);
    color: var(--cream);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .cta-btn:hover { background: var(--accent-light); }
</style>
